content: Nevermore-Ray: Contributed significantly to plugin development, merging two substantial PRs: #2797 "btcfun Plugin for Eliza" (+118,412/-7,054 lines) and #2643 "chore(update-plugin-initialization): btcfun & trikon plugin" (+124,255/-8,248 lines). Currently has an open PR #2911 for additional Btcfun support. Activity was concentrated on just 3 days this month, primarily focused on configuration files (46%) and code changes (32%), with a total of 5 commits modifying 837 files.
